.Dd June 24, 2026
.Dt X11DND_END_DRAG 3
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm x11dnd_end_drag
.Nd end a drag operation normally
.Sh LIBRARY
.Lb libx11dnd
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.In x11dnd.h
.Ft void
.Fn x11dnd_end_drag "X11DndSourceSession *sess"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Fn x11dnd_end_drag
ends a drag operation normally, typically after
.Li XdndFinished
has been received from the target or the drop is otherwise complete.
It releases the source session and frees any associated resources.
.Pp
The session handle
.Fa sess
is invalid after this call.
Passing
.Dv NULL
is safe and results in a no-op.
.Pp
For cancelling a drag before the drop completes, see
.Xr x11dnd_cancel_drag 3 .
.Sh RETURN VALUES
None.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr x11dnd_start_drag 3 ,
.Xr x11dnd_cancel_drag 3 ,
.Xr x11dnd 3
